bayou.mime

Class MultipartParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • bayou.mime.MultipartParser

  • public class MultipartParser
extends Object
    Parses a multipart body.

    Given a sequence of bytes in the multipart format (see RFC2046), this class parses it into parts.
